Vicky Cristina Barcelona;;74;;81;;PG-13;;Americans Vicky (Rebecca Hall) and Cristina (Scarlett Johansson) arrive in Spain for a summer vacation at a friend's (Patricia Clarkson) Barcelona home. Visiting an art gallery, they meet seductive painter Juan Antonio (Javier Bardem), who invites them for a weekend of food, art and sex. Sparks really ignite when his fiery former lover (Penélope Cruz) arrives on the scene, making for a very crowded house.;;Drama,Comedy,Romance;;Woody Allen;;2008;;Javier Bardem,Patricia Clarkson,Penélope Cruz,Kevin Dunn,Rebecca Hall,Scarlett Johansson,Chris Messina,Carrie Preston,Pablo Schreiber,Zak Orth,Abel Folk,Christopher Evan Welch;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vicky_cristina_barcelona